//A level 5 spell that allows you to take control of an ogre if it fails a spell saving throw (works on ogres, ogre mages, and ogrelings (IDS class) but not on half-ogres)

//A spell that grants the ability to vanish like the ôvanishing beastö as soon as a hit is taken (teleport field effect, so random, within 10 meters, so annoying)